OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FA 14-year-old girl has been found
OL,8,Fguilty of the attempted murder of two
OL,9,Fteachers and a pupil during a frenzied
OL,10,Fknife attack at a school in Ammanford.
OL,12,FA jury at Swansea Crown Court failed
OL,13,Fto believe the 14-year-old did not
OL,14,Fintend to kill teachers Fiona Elias,
OL,15,FElizabeth Hopkin, and a pupil at Ysgol
OL,16,FDyffryn Aman on 24 April 2024 last
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FMs Hopkin was airlifted to hospital
OL,20,Fafter suffering a stab wound to her
OL,21,Fneck.
