OL,7,FAt the same time, Ms Elias received
OL,8,Finjuries to her arms and hand and was
OL,9,Ftaken to Morriston Hospital along with
OL,10,Fa pupil who was stabbed in the
OL,11,Fshoulder.
OL,13,FFollowing the verdict, Judge Paul
OL,14,FThomas KC told the girl, who cannot be
OL,15,Fnamed for legal reasons, that he would
OL,16,Fadjourn sentencing until 28 April for
OL,17,Fthe preparation of pre-sentence
OL,18,Freports, including a psychology report.
