OL,7,FAddressing the defendant, the judge
OL,8,Fsaid is taking the time as he "needs
OL,9,Fto get it right."JTeacher Fiona Elias
OL,10,Fsaid, "The nightmare and trauma
OL,11,Fexperienced will not end today with a
OL,12,Fguilty verdict."
OL,14,F"I would like to thank my family and
OL,15,Ffriends who have supported me through
OL,16,Fsuch a difficult time and of course
OL,17,Fthe fantastic community at Ysgol
OL,18,FDyffryn Aman.
