OL,7,FDuring the trial, the court heard how
OL,8,Fthe defendant had an attraction to
OL,9,Fcarrying knives.
OL,11,FShe told a jury she took a knife to
OL,12,Fschool with her every day.
OL,14,FShe would carry kitchen knives in her
OL,15,Fbag as a way of combating bullying she
OL,16,Fsaid she experienced inside and
OL,17,Foutside of school.
