OL,7,FIn September 2023, while attending
OL,8,FYsgol Dyffryn Aman, the teenager was
OL,9,Ffound carrying a knife during a search
OL,10,Fof her belongings.
OL,12,FThe teacher who carried out that
OL,13,Fsearch was Ms Elias.
OL,15,FThe then 13-year-old girl was
OL,16,Fsuspended from school for a week and
OL,17,Fallowed to return on the condition her
OL,18,Ffather checked her school bag each
OL,19,Fmorning and removed dangerous knives
OL,20,Ffrom the house.
