OL,7,FHowever, her father failed to check
OL,8,Fher bag on the fateful morning of 24
OL,9,FApril 2024.
OL,11,FIn her pocket, the girl would smuggle
OL,12,Fa multi-tool knife used by her father
OL,13,Ffor fishing.
OL,15,FThe target of her attack ` Ms Elias.
OL,17,F'Crime of a Lifetime'
