OL,7,FThe court heard the defendant
OL,8,Fchillingly wrote in a notebook that
OL,9,Fshe would 'commit the crime of a
OL,10,Flifetime'.
OL,12,FThe notebook also contained a drawing
OL,13,Fof Ms Elias in which she referred to
OL,14,Fher as 'frog face'.
OL,16,FThe defendant told the court she
OL,17,Fstrongly disliked Ms Elias and would
OL,18,Fjoke with her friends about
OL,19,F'assaulting' the Assistant Head
OL,20,FTeacher.
