OL,7,FOn the morning of the attack, an
OL,8,Fencounter with Ms Elias would send the
OL,9,Fknife-carrying girl into a rage.
OL,11,FThe teacher told her she should not be
OL,12,Fin the lower school hall during the
OL,13,Fbreak period.
OL,15,FThe girl admitted this made her
OL,16,F'angry' and she would later tell
OL,17,Ffriends she was 'going to do something
OL,18,Fstupid'.
OL,20,F'I Want to Kill You'
