OL,7,FThe teenage girl would follow Ms Elias
OL,8,Fonto the yard, confronting her and
OL,9,Ffellow teacher Ms Hopkin.
OL,11,FCCTV played to the court showed the
OL,12,Fmoment the defendant lunged at Ms
OL,13,FElias with the knife she had concealed
OL,14,Fin her pocket.
OL,16,FDuring the attack, in which the young
OL,17,Fgirl slashed at Ms Elias' arms and
OL,18,Fhand, the court was told she screamed,
OL,19,F"I want to f****** kill you."
