OL,7,FMs Hopkin tried to save her colleague
OL,8,Ffrom the knife attack but she was
OL,9,Fstabbed in the neck.
OL,11,FMale members of staff would try to
OL,12,Fintervene to subdue the teenage girl,
OL,13,Falthough they couldn't stop her from
OL,14,Frunning at another pupil and stabbing
OL,15,Fthe pupil in the shoulder, before
OL,16,Ffinally being disarmed.
