OL,7,FThe stabbings threw the school into
OL,8,Flockdown, with hundreds of worried and
OL,9,Fconcerned parents gathering at the
OL,10,Fschool gates for hours, waiting for
OL,11,Fnews.
OL,13,F'One Way to be a Celebrity'
OL,15,FAs paramedics took away the teachers
OL,16,Fand pupil, the defendant was placed in
OL,17,Fthe back of a police van.
