OL,7,FThe jury was told, while under
OL,8,Fcaution, that the defendant remarked,
OL,9,F"That's one way to be a celebrity,"
OL,10,Fand that she was, "Ninety per cent
OL,11,Fsure she would be on the news."
OL,13,FWhile giving evidence, both teachers
OL,14,Fdescribed how they thought they were
OL,15,F'going to die' during the assault.
OL,17,FThe defendant insisted she never
OL,18,Fwanted to kill anyone during the
OL,19,Fattack, admitting she had very little
OL,20,Frecollection of the events that led to
OL,21,Fher stabbing three people.
