OL,7,FIt took a jury three and a half hours
OL,8,Fto reach their verdict of guilty on
OL,9,Fall charges.
OL,11,FThe judge said he would adjourn
OL,12,Fsentencing until April 28 for the
OL,13,Fpreparation of pre-sentence reports,
OL,14,Fincluding a psychology report.
OL,16,FThe judge Paul Thomas KC thanked the
OL,17,Fjury for their work in a "difficult
OL,18,Fand unusual" trial.
