OL,7,F"At the end of the day if she was not
OL,8,Fa 14-year-old girl and had been an
OL,9,Fadult the most likely outcome would
OL,10,Fhave been a life sentence," he said.
OL,12,F'Clear Message For Pupils', Teacher
OL,13,FSays
OL,15,FFollowing the verdict, teacher Ms
OL,16,FElias said, "This verdict today should
OL,17,Fbe seen as a clear message for pupils
OL,18,Facross the country.
