OL,7,F"I would not want any other individual
OL,8,Fto go through the nightmare that I
OL,9,Fhave endured over the last nine months.
OL,11,F"The nightmare and trauma experienced
OL,12,Fwill not end today with a guilty
OL,13,Fverdict.
OL,15,F"I would like to thank my family and
OL,16,Ffriends who have supported me through
OL,17,Fsuch a difficult time and of course
OL,18,Fthe fantastic community at Ysgol
OL,19,FDyffryn Aman.
